description:
Hey, I'm Pineapowl

My mummy is a Pineapple and my daddy is an owl.

My friends and I like to fly, we eat forest fruits and tender shoots and help those who can't reach the sky.

Each pineapowl you collect gives the holder a chance to win a physical 1of1 carving. (50 total unique 1of1's)

Each wood spirit can be ornamental, charm or keyring.

20% community homeless outreach donation.
